[Student "S"]
{With 14 points, \C shortage, and support for the other suits NORTH makes a Takeout Double.

SOUTH has 13 points so she bids 2\C. This is an artificial bid, apprising NORTH of SOUTH's opening 
hand strength, and forcing the partnership to reach the game level.

NORTH sugggests \Hs as trumps. 
SOUTH doesn't like \Hs so she suggests \Ss. 
NORTH agrees with \Ss and bids game, 4\S.}

